About this item

  • 【Wireless Charging Lamp】 LED Wireless charger desk lamp has a built-in battery capacity of 1200mAH, providing 15W fast wireless charging for your cell phone. Just place your phone in the charging induction area for a quick and efficient charge. This eliminates the need for cumbersome charging wires and keeps your phone charged at all times
  • 【Bluetooth Speaker Charger】 The wireless bluetooth speaker function is straightforward and convenient to operate, easily establishing a stable connection with cell phones, tablets,computers, and other devices. The high-quality music, remarkable bass effect, coupled with music ambient lighting effects, delivers the ultimate music enjoyment experience
  • 【Alarm Clock for Bedrooms】 The alarm clocks is equipped with a clear LED display, which can display the current time. The bedside alarm clock has built-in 2 different white noises, including rain, birdsong, which can help you unwind and get better sleep. And alarm clocks can be set to allow you to wake up on time every morning
  • 【Colorful Atmosphere Lights】 This wireless charger atmosphere lamp has built-in 7 kinds of colorful atmosphere lights, and you can choose different lighting effects according to your preferences and scenes. Whether it is a party, family gathering or relaxing time, desk lamp with wireless charger can create a pleasant atmosphere
  • 【Multi Functional Integration】 New G-shaped design, bluetooth speaker alarm clock not only ambient light, but also music ringtone, sleep lamp, sunrise wake-up lamp, atmosphere lamp, bedside lamp, dazzling light effect, FM audio, clock, etc. This night light with wireless speaker is suitable for bedside, bedroom, living room, home decor and office for any occasion, whether it's Thanksgiving, Christmas, birthday, Father's Day, Mother's Day or New Year

How customer reviews and ratings work

Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

Amazon Customer
4 out of 5 stars
Works, but a little Complicated to Use
This is a nice light, wireless charger, and Bluetooth speaker. It looks and works as suggested, and it feels sturdy and is of good quality.It looks nice, the light and shape of it provide an interesting effect. There are many different colors that you change by pressing the button to the far right. The Bluetooth setup was easy, and it pairs like any Bluetooth device.The only issue is that I find this complicated to use. I had trouble getting the time from military to standard, and there are a few too many settings on this for me.

  • Dana E. Cameron
    3.0 out of 5 stars Decent Features but Lighting Issues
    Reviewed in the United States on March 2, 2025
    Color: WhiteAmazon Vine Customer Review of Free Product( What's this? )
    This is a gimmicky lamp that has some good features, but some significant flaws too. On the positive side, the controls are very intuitive and user-friendly, which makes it simple to use right out of the box. The wireless phone charging works pretty well. It pairs effortlessly with your phone, which you can then use to control the speaker volume. Music sounds pretty decent, surprisingly for such a small speaker. Much less tinny than I was expecting. Unfortunately, several of the lighting settings flicker badly, which is distracting and takes away from the overall experience. Another downside is that it requires a USB plug for power, so you can’t just plug it straight into a wall outlet.

  • Pamela Walker
    1.0 out of 5 stars Horrible instructions, crappy sound
    Reviewed in the United States on December 24, 2024
    Color: WhiteAmazon Vine Customer Review of Free Product( What's this? )
    This item promises a lot and delivers very little. I don't know what to call it, because the only thing that works really well is the colored light. But, since I didn't order it for the lamp, I'm very disappointed.

    I mainly got it for the cell phone charging feature. I like the idea of being able to just sit my phone down and have it charge, rather than having to plug it in. However I was never able to get that feature to work.

    It was difficult to get anything to work, because the instructions were so bad. First off, they were very small and I had to get a magnifying glass to read them. They were worse than basic -- they were confusing and convoluted. The buttons on the gadget itself didn't help much either, because most were not common symbols and they were hard to see; the flush-mounted buttons were the same color as the background, with a thin indent for the symbol. [see my photo] Taking a picture with my phone and enlarging it was the only way I could even see what the symbols were and I still couldn't decipher what some of them meant.

    By randomly pushing buttons, I was able to get the sounds going. The sounds were horrible. Chirping birds were at a pitch that was actually painful. What I think was supposed to be waves on a beach sounded like a car motor running. I was never able to operate the radio, but I cannot imagine that the sound would have been pleasant to listen to.

    The item is very big for my bedside table. That's not their fault, the description of it did say that it was over 8 by 8 inches, but I didn't catch that.

    I think this item gets my FAIL Award of the Year.
    Read more
